00:26:11.173 --> 00:26:12.462
Stay in the Word.

00:26:17.451 --> 00:26:17.908
The Word of God keeps you grounded.

00:26:17.908 --> 00:26:23.440
Stay in the Word; it keeps you grounded, baby.

00:26:23.440 --> 00:26:25.600
Don't get off in weirdness.

