00:26:49.689 --> 00:26:56.799
I hope I did that right, but you've got to have a balance.

00:27:08.270 --> 00:27:08.730
It's an equilibrium: making sure that you stay grounded, you have the word, you have the spirit, and you keep things flowing.

00:27:15.004 --> 00:27:15.396
I talked too much; Braden told me 25 minutes.

00:27:15.396 --> 00:27:33.973
