Any other time of the day is good, but there is a Holy Ghost flow at night.

00:28:40.979 --> 00:29:24.870
I was watching somebody special; they were talking about why in the old days they would have two times of sleep.

00:29:24.880 --> 00:30:18.640
They would sleep from 6:00 at night to about 11:00, wake up, have another little meal, pray until they call it the second watch or something.

00:30:23.360 --> 00:30:24.240
I was watching it and I was like, "Get out of here!

00:30:24.240 --> 00:31:02.580
" They would have the candles and they would pray, and they said this was how culture was back then.

00:31:02.580 --> 00:32:00.959
They would have a little meal and they would put the firewood on the fireplace and stay up from 11:00 to about 2:00 or 3:00 and then they would go back to bed.

00:32:49.040 --> 00:32:50.240
I thought they knew something.

00:33:43.555 --> 00:33:43.832
It was some people in the Dark Ages.

00:33:43.832 --> 00:33:59.590
I was just like, you know, when we got modern electricity, we don't do stuff like that anymore because we have lights.

