We believe, Father, that we walk in that divine blessing.

00:39:09.111 --> 00:39:14.996
As He is, so are we in this world, Lord.

00:39:14.996 --> 00:39:21.660
We take this right now in the mighty name of Jesus.

00:39:21.660 --> 00:39:29.589
